I don't know what you guys imagine,

00:00:58.080 --> 00:01:02.000
but this might be some of the images that come to mind.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:04.839
But the reality is that most of Colombia looks like this.

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:07.360
If you've ever been to Colombia,

00:01:07.360 --> 00:01:09.040
I don't know how many of you guys have been to Colombia.

00:01:09.040 --> 00:01:09.879
Maybe raise your hand.

00:01:09.879 --> 00:01:11.639
Ah, a couple.

00:01:11.639 --> 00:01:13.879
It looks mostly like this, right?

00:01:13.879 --> 00:01:16.459
And this sort of terrain leads

00:01:16.459 --> 00:01:19.160
to some very particular challenges,

00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:21.199
specifically in healthcare.

00:01:21.199 --> 00:01:24.959
So, Colombian healthcare is very particular.

